📌 What Is This?
This workspace uses three AI prompting files in the utils/ folder to create a complete, production-ready automated test suite for the CND (Connect & Discovery) web application — without writing a single line of code manually.

The lifecycle follows a 3-Step Prompting Pipeline, where the output of one step feeds directly into the next.

🗂️ The Three Prompting Files
#	File	Role	When to Use
1️⃣	applicationAnalysisGuidelines.txt	Application Analyst	First — Understand the app
2️⃣	testGenerationGuidelines.txt	Test Case Engineer	Second — Design test cases
3️⃣	CucumberTestGenerator.txt	Automation Coder	Third — Generate Java code
💡 Bonus: CNDApplicationGuidlines.txt(optional).txt is a CND-specific supplement used alongside Step 1 to give the AI deeper context about the CND application's navigation patterns and UI structure.

