💡 Tips for Best Results
Always run Step 1 first when working with a new or updated module — never skip app analysis.
Use the optional CND guidelines alongside Step 1 for faster, more accurate navigation flows.
Feed Step 1 output directly into Step 2 as context — this is what makes the test cases precise.
One module at a time — generate test cases per module for better accuracy and traceability.
Review JSON before Step 3 — validate test steps make sense before generating Java code.
Always compile after Step 3 — catch errors early with mvn clean test-compile.
